headline: Snowflake Names Stella Low as Chief Communications Officer
summary: No-Headquarters/BOZEMAN, Mont., September 29, 2025--Snowflake (NYSE: SNOW), the AI Data Cloud company, announced today that Stella Low is joining the company as Chief Communications Officer on October 6th. As part of the leadership team, Ms. Low will be responsible for Snowflake’s communications strategy, advising the company’s leadership as Snowflake continues to grow and scale as a technology leader.
